{"tid":957682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"油美苑裝修工人 搭棚期間墮平台不治","createTime":"2018-12-27T08:13:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T08:34:56.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3967bf68e27040d918b061d9967884d6e200a1cb","tid":957682,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T08:13:30.000Z","msg":"【15:06】墮樓亡工人年約50歲，剛首天到油美苑開工，他在鑽狗臂架準備搭棚期間墮下。<br />\n<br />\n油塘油美苑濤美閣，中午1時21分，一名裝修工人工作期間，意外跌落一樓平台，頭部淌血重創，血流披面，安全帽亦跌在地上，工友見狀報警求助，救護員到場將受傷昏迷工人送院治理，惜最終搶救不治，警方正調查事件。據了解，死者今天到上址首天開工，安裝狗臂架準備搭棚進行維修，當時有戴安全帽，亦有安全繩，懷疑安全繩斷裂而墮下慘死。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n房署在現場地面圍起鐵欄，準備做外牆維修工程，《蘋果》所見，部份樓層的電梯大堂石屎剝落，其中9樓遺下一條斷開的尼龍繩，暫未知涉事工人是否由該樓層墮到平台。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181227/59075038\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181227%2F59075038&d=cxYmfqVuV6muW8ojATK39k%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=5c138876\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181227%2F59075038&h=42be5112\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181227/59075038</a>"},{"pid":"fa668b11e663370f48e06b7bd4a4e475c016a680","tid":957682,"uid":146726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T08:21:27.000Z","msg":"尼龍繩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb6ec2e6abf54fe330f4456277fb998dfa979c10","tid":957682,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T08:23:03.000Z","msg":"尼龍繩...咁不如拎條電線啦"},{"pid":"2e7eaaeb4d66c345a407ed744843efd4822251bb","tid":957682,"uid":4384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb6ec2e6abf54fe330f4456277fb998dfa979c10","tid":957682,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T08:23:03.000Z","msg":"尼龍繩...咁不如拎條電線啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T08:29:16.000Z"